data.description:
**Buyers ask your agent to inquire about the 3% FHA assumable loan** 
This Holly Hills home blends inviting warmth with a coveted locale. A covered front patio welcomes residents into a light-filled interior renovated in 2020. New flooring extends throughout an easily flowing layout as abundant brightness streams in through new windows. An open living area offers ample space for both relaxing and entertaining. Lined w/ a wall of cabinetry, a dining area opens into an updated kitchen w/ new stainless steel appliances. Built-in shelving surrounds a fireplace in a cozy den w/ sliding glass doors opening to a covered patio with a large private backyard. Three main-level bedrooms include a primary w/ an en-suite bath. Downstairs, a finished basement offers a large rec room and a fourth bedroom. An ideal location affords proximity to I-25 w/ less than ten minutes to Cherry Creek, Park Meadows and DTC areas. Residents can walk to the High Line Canal Trail, Colorado Athletic Club, Bible Park, & Yale Light Rail Station, with shopping and dining conveniently located just steps away!
